description: Welcome to the luxury residences at Pier 4. This rare, beautifully designed condo is one of finest 2 bedroom units available today.  This 2019 construction is surrounded by water on three sides and anchored by a one-acre green park. It was meticulously designed with an emphasis of modern contemporary design that stands out from the rest. This sophisticated and luxurious home has 2 beds/2.5 baths and close to 1400 sqft. Features include; large gourmet modern kitchen with Gaggenau stainless steel appliances, over sized bedrooms, ensuite baths, and a sun-drenched living room that overlooks private ~ balcony with gorgeous views of the water and new Fidelity Seaport World Trade Center. Amenities include: valet or self -parking, personal concierge services, a dog spa, fitness/wellness center, golf simulator, a private lounge with gas fireplace, catering pantry & kitchen with adjoining terrace equipped with grill, fire pit & wet bar overlooking the water. Come make this your new home.
